            "html": "This swarm of thousands of fist-sized ticks forms a moving carpet of bloated insects\u2014a nauseating and intimidating sight."
        },
        {
            "name": "Tick",
            "type": "section",
            "sections": [
                {
                    "name": "Tick Diseases",
                    "type": "section",
